      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for a fantastic ride! This vehicle is in great shape and has been clearly well-maintained over the years. It offers a smooth, reliable driving experience and a clean, comfortable interior that makes every trip a pleasure. While you might find a few minor signs of normal use, it's a solid, high-quality car that's ready for many more miles of adventure!",
