    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you will find some minor stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster and floor mats. Mechanically, the car is sound, starts reliably, and has a documented history of routine oil changes and service intervals. It offers a dependable driving experience for someone looking for a quality vehicle that has many miles of service left to give.",
      "price": 36500.0,
